            "text": "$(item)Torchpowder/$ can be $(concept)Compacted/$ to form $(item)Blazing Ingots/$. The ingots can then be $(concept)Pressed/$ to form $(item)Blazing Sheets/$, and then $(concept)Rolled/$ into $(item)Blazing Rods/$."
